annotations.title: 4 Favorite Brandy Cocktails

textContent:
2oz (60ml) Brandy
.75oz (22.5ml) Elderflower Liqueur
.75oz (22.5ml) Lemon Juice
.25oz (7.5ml) Cinnamon Syrup
.25oz (7.5ml) Balsamic Vinegar
1 Strawberry
Garnish Half Strawberry

Muddle strawberry
Shake with ice cubes
Strain into rocks glass and top with crushed ice
